TimeBombs Important Readme
==========================

This demo contains four exclusive levels from the full version of TimeBombs
that will be available in July. In order to run this demo you will require 
the following system specification:

+ OS 3.0
+ 2 Megs Chip
+ 1 Megs Fast
+ 68020+ Processor
+ Hard Drive recommended

The full version of TimeBombs will contain:

+ More massive and exciting levels including many secret ones.
+ More and improved graphics
+ A Different sound track per level
+ Hard Disk installer

                                   .oOo.

If you would like to pre-register this game and receive the full versions 
of Visions and EAC, then please send £10 to the following address:

ENGiNE NiNE DESiGN
50 Thicket Drive
Maltby
Rotherham
South Yorkshire
S66 7LB
U.K.

Please note that TimeBombs will not be available until 1st July 1999. EAC 
and Visions however, will be sent to you immediately.


